Adding to its lineup an alternate-history drama that has been hotly anticipated by viewers and critics alike, the Showtime network will premiere an original series Sunday night that examines how the course of world events would have been altered if the Nazis had won the 1991 NBA Finals.According to press materials, the new show, called , explores what might have happened had a Third Reich team led by Adolf Hitler defeated Michael Jordan and the Chicago Bulls to take home the NBA title.